<Aman and swarna sits on a divider>

Maya : Mundhe cheppalsindhi , nadhe tappu..
Aman : U.S deniki 
Maya : Computer science M.S seat vacchindhi
Aman : Study kosam ae ga, Kurchoni matladithe set aipothadhi le
Aman : Ekkadiki vellipoyadu eedu…. mobile switched off vastundhi 
Maya : Okkasari elaaina matladali aman. just once.
Aman : Sare padha velli vethukudham..
< Asheesh be waiting outside a house while maya comes throught the gate and nods her head in regret.>
< Asheesh calls everyone he knows >

Aman : Nuvvu inka vellu .. Somehow i’ll find him. Atleast call cheyyamani chepta..
<disperse>
